               <code code="34067-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="INDICATIONS &amp; USAGE SECTION"/>
               <title>INDICATIONS AND USAGE</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Quflora<sup>®</sup> FE Pediatric Liquid Drops is a prescription dietary supplement providing essential vitamins, iron and fluoride.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20170419"/>
            </section>
